@startuml
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 80
skinparam ranksep 60
top to bottom direction

' Main flow
NeoCommonSearchApplication -down-> interceptor : Start flow
interceptor -down-> controller : Extract request id
controller -down-> service : Calls method
service -down-> repository : Calls method
repository -down-> config : Uses DB connection

' Combined data package
repository -down-> data : Returns entity
service -down-> data : Uses mapper, gets DTO
controller -down-> data : Sends DTO as response

' Exception handling (red dashed)
service .[#red,dashed,thickness=2].> exception : Throws to GlobalExceptionHandler
repository .[#red,dashed,thickness=2].> exception : Throws to GlobalExceptionHandler
exception --> logging

' Utils usage (dotted)
controller ..down-> utils : Uses utility methods
service ..down-> utils : Uses utility methods

@enduml